{"tid":1019303,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"新移民其實都係社會垃圾","createTime":"2019-02-13T00:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T14:48:41.000Z","uid":104804,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e07b0011815ea4e630248a99657f6bf5a2c6f249","tid":1019303,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T00:09:38.000Z","msg":"依家中國咁勁<br />\n有錢有知識點會仲爭住黎香港<br />\n北京政治中心最多mnc/政府總部<br />\n上海金融中心<br />\n深圳it中心<br />\n廣州進出口中心<br />\n你係叻既話呢幾個城市都可以創一番天地<br />\n我識個河南朋友無家底<br />\n依家深圳做緊big4一萬幾人仔一個月<br />\n揾到個香港offer三萬港紙都放棄左<br />\n佢覺得深圳發展適合佢<br />\n自己唔了解香港環境無必要去爭<br />\n呢種人去到邊都有人要有發展機會<br />\n但黎香港新移民都係大陸最窮個班<br />\n好多嫁個廢老落黎為醫療為綜援<br />\n最好帶埋成條村黎香港拿福利<br />\n但佢地從來無諗過發奮圖強<br />\n只係識做社會垃圾<br />\n黎到香港做譚仔就可以高人工過香港大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021ef0705b09ed8da41ba04761097dfb81bfb49c","tid":1019303,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T00:43:37.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6997aa00574bb7e99fc607caea365ccbbd67d8","tid":1019303,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"021ef0705b09ed8da41ba04761097dfb81bfb49c","tid":1019303,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T00:43:37.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T00:52:30.000Z","msg":"本來失業<br />\n依家仲有得撈多幾個月"},{"pid":"211def812f454a8db711c3bb4ca5cf01c40b3521","tid":1019303,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa6997aa00574bb7e99fc607caea365ccbbd67d8","tid":1019303,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"021ef0705b09ed8da41ba04761097dfb81bfb49c","tid":1019303,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T00:43:37.000Z","msg